<div class="row u-mb-5">
   <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h1>Typography</h1>
    <p>Proxima Nova is the primary font used in Buoy. The baseline font-size is <code>1 rem</code> which is equivalent to <code>16px</code>. The <code>body</code> has a line-height of <code>1.5</code> to establish vertical rhythm.</p>
   </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-5">
   <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h2>Headers</h2> 
    <p>Headers have fixed bottom margins which should not be modified. <code>h1</code> tags should be used a maximum of one time per page.</p> 
   </div>
</div>


